      "ref": "1.1",
      "chapter": 1,
      "sanskrit": "Dukkha",
      "transliteration": "",
      "text": "Birth is suffering, aging is suffering, illness is suffering, death is suffering, union with what is displeasing is suffering, separation from what is pleasing is suffering. In brief, the five aggregates are suffering.",
